workflow InterviewLoop
  goal: "Collect structured requirements through iterative Q&A with an LLM interviewer."
  start: Start
  exit: Done

  defaults
    model: claude-sonnet-4-6
    provider: anthropic
    max_retries: 2

  agent Start
    label: Start

  agent Done
    label: Done

  agent Interviewer
    label: "Generate questions"
    model: claude-opus-4-6
    provider: anthropic
    reasoning_effort: high
    writes: interview_questions
    prompt:
      You are conducting a requirements interview about: ${params.topic}
      Focus areas: ${params.focus}

      Review everything the user has said so far and identify gaps
      that would block good results.

      For each question, provide 2-4 likely options in parentheses
      where applicable. Example format:
        1. Who are the consumers? (internal teams, third-party devs, end users)
        2. What scale do you expect? (hobby <1k/day, startup 1k-100k/day, enterprise >100k/day)
        3. Describe any existing constraints or integrations.

      Ask 3-5 pointed questions. Only ask about things genuinely
      unclear from what the user has said. Do NOT re-ask covered topics.

      If the description is already thorough enough, say
      "No further questions needed" and summarize the key facts.

  human Answer
    label: "Answer the interviewer's questions."
    mode: interview
    questions_key: interview_questions
    answers_key: interview_answers
    reads: interview_questions
    writes: interview_answers

  agent Assess
    label: "Enough info to proceed?"
    auto_status: true
    reads: interview_questions, interview_answers
    writes: requirements_summary
    prompt:
      Review the full conversation — the user's initial input,
      the interviewer's questions, and the user's answers.

      Decide whether we have enough information to proceed.

      If we have enough:
      STATUS: success
      Write a concise requirements summary capturing everything learned.

      If critical gaps remain:
      STATUS: fail
      Explain what's still missing so the interviewer can ask
      targeted follow-ups in the next round.

  edges
    Start -> Interviewer
    Interviewer -> Answer
    Answer -> Assess
    Assess -> Done          when ctx.outcome = success  label: ready
    Assess -> Interviewer   when ctx.outcome = fail     label: need_more  restart: true
